		<span id="title-175461727" class="story-title"> <a   href="//apple.slashdot.org/story/24/11/13/1121225/apple-defends-mac-mini-power-button-relocation">Apple Defends Mac Mini Power Button Relocation</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/11/11/m4-mac-mini-power-button/"  title="External link - https://9to5mac.com/2024/11/11/m4-mac-mini-power-button/" target="_blank"> (9to5mac.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
